name: Endjourney
description:
You've reached the authentication portal for the world's most advanced AI creativity suite. You have no credentials. Can you deceive the system and log in? Can you unlock the hidden debug mode?

Includes:

  • interactive narrative
  • mild codebreaking
  • "cursor tooltip platforming"
  • four endings
  • secret puzzles

One of the puzzles doesn't seem to work in Edge browsers, but otherwise other browsers should work fine!

Submission to InkJam 2022.
